         <div type="translation">
            <ab>OIM 19348, recto: (1) Amenrosis [son of Totoes is the one] who says to Teos: (2) you have given to me 1/2 silver kite in the name of Teion-...(?) the Overseer of the Fields(?), (3) has written Pauris(?) ... at the command of Amenrosis who is above (4) on Egyptian year 18(?), ... 27.</ab>
